message: To reliably get 25 points, find two ingredients with the same 'lives on' feature (e.g., two land animals or two water animals). message: To succeed, first combine two animals from the same environment (e.g., two water animals). Next, use the 'growth serum' on this new hybrid. Then, combine the 'grown' hybrid with an animal from a *different* environment (e.g., a land animal if your hybrid is aquatic). This sequence yields the highest positive values (around 30-35). *Do not* add a third environment type (e.g., air animal to a land/water hybrid), as this drastically lowers the value. The 'mutation catalyst' also consistently led to negative values in my attempts, so I recommend avoiding it.
